#CAMERA 3
#phrase Hero 3
A fiery tiger, a nightmare offspring of the astral. Strikes terror into the hearts of enemies, with only one appearance. Hearing his heartbreaking roar, people scatter in panic. Well, the daredevils who decided to slay the beast are doomed to a painful death. For just 15,000, you can become the master of this incarnation of fire and death.